U.S. Coast Guard Prepares for Tsunami to Strike Hawaii, Urges Evacuations

-- B y   S t e v e n   M c P h e r s o n
-- 
2011-03-11T08:38:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/u-s-coast-guard-prepares-for-tsunami-to-strike-hawaii-urges-evacuations.html
The U.S. Coast Guard is preparing
to provide post-tsunami support in  Hawaii . The first wave is
expected at 2:59 a.m., the agency said in a release. It urged
residents in flood zones to prepare to evacuate.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
